Dear Hiring Team,

I am applying for the *Applications Engineer* role at *Particle Measuring Systems*. I bring more than three years of experience building production software systems that translate complex requirements into reliable workflows, plus a Master of Science in Computer Science from Pace University. More importantly for this role, I have spent my career turning technical detail into systems, documentation, and support that non-specialists can act on.

